OL,3,CInquests into breast surgeon Ian
OL,4,CPaterson to cost more than #6.5 million
OL,6,FWords by Midlands Correspondent Stacey
OL,7,FFoster and ITV News Producer Cat
OL,8,FDinneny
OL,10,FThe inquests into disgraced breast
OL,11,Fsurgeon Ian Paterson's patients are
OL,12,Fexpected to cost more than #6.5
OL,13,Fmillion, ITV News has learned.
OL,15,FThe inquests, which are currently
OL,16,Fsuspended, started in October last
OL,17,Fyear and are examining the deaths of
OL,18,F62 women who were operated on by
OL,19,FPaterson and later died of breast
OL,20,Fcancer.
