OL,6,FSo far, only one inquest has
OL,7,Fconcluded, and it found that the woman
OL,8,Fin question wasn't even operated on by
OL,9,FPaterson.
OL,11,FNow, an investigation into the cost of
OL,12,Fthe inquests, obtained via Freedom of
OL,13,FInformation requests submitted by ITV
OL,14,FNews, has revealed:
OL,16,FThe costs all relate to the
OL,17,Fadministration of the inquests,
OL,18,Fincluding fees for the coroner, legal
OL,19,Fcounsel, solicitors and legal teams
OL,20,Frepresenting the NHS.
