OL,6,FShirley Moroney, whose sister Marie
OL,7,Fwas operated on by Paterson and who
OL,8,Fdied in 2008, said: "It's just
OL,9,Fshocking, and that's just the tip of
OL,10,Fthe iceberg."
OL,12,FPaterson was found guilty of 17 counts
OL,13,Fof wounding patients with intent,
OL,14,Fagainst 10 victims, at Nottingham
OL,15,FCrown Court in 2017.
OL,17,FHe was initially handed a 15-year
OL,18,Fprison term, but Court of Appeal
OL,19,Fjudges increased his tariff to 20
OL,20,Fyears in 2018.
