OL,6,FThese inquests are now the fifth
OL,7,Finvestigation into his practices
OL,8,Ffollowing two independent reports, a
OL,9,Fcriminal trial and one government
OL,10,Finquiry.
OL,12,FNot a single inquest has been heard so
OL,13,Ffar this year, with several hearings
OL,14,Fcancelled, leaving families in limbo.
OL,16,FShirley added: "You're constantly
OL,17,Fliving on the edge of when will this
OL,18,Fbe over? The 17th and 18th March were
OL,19,Fgoing to be my opportunity to have
OL,20,FMarie's case heard and cathartically
OL,21,Flet go of some of the pain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
