OL,6,F"He's not in prison because of Marie
OL,7,F(dying), and that's why we're at the
OL,8,FCoroner's Court. Clearly somebody
OL,9,Fsuspected there was something more to
OL,10,Fthis than just Marie dying of breast
OL,11,Fcancer."
OL,13,FPaterson's 14-year campaign of botched
OL,14,Fand unnecessary surgery was conducted
OL,15,Fat hospitals both public and private
OL,16,Facross Birmingham and Solihull.
OL,18,FIn 2020, there was an inquiry which
OL,19,Fheard Paterson had been carrying out
OL,20,Fan unapproved version of a mastectomy,
OL,21,Fleaving some breast tissue behind.
