OL,11,FFour years later, around 650 cases of
OL,12,Fwomen who'd had the so-called cleavage
OL,13,Fsparing mastectomy were sent to the
OL,14,Fcoroner over concerns they had died
OL,15,Fprematurely, of which 62 were opened.
OL,17,FHearings started in October last year,
OL,18,Fbut they've been paused since January
OL,19,Fover claims of bias and disagreements
OL,20,Famong the medical experts. Individual
OL,21,Finquests are due to resume in June.
