OL,6,FDan Hudson's mother, Gillian, died of
OL,7,Fbreast cancer in 2022. She had a
OL,8,Fcleavage sparing mastectomy performed
OL,9,Fby Ian Paterson.
OL,11,FHe told ITV News: "How can you
OL,12,Fpossibly justify spending #6.5 million
OL,13,Ffor no reason? They must think there's
OL,14,Fa reason.
OL,16,F"The main issue is this is just going
OL,17,Fon and on and on and on. We're going
OL,18,Fto end up in a situation where
OL,19,Fpotentially Ian Paterson comes out of
OL,20,Fprison and then what's to stop him
OL,21,Fjust legging it?"
