OL,6,F"There's probably been public pressure
OL,7,Fto hold the inquest anyway and from
OL,8,Fthat point of view, maybe they just
OL,9,Fhad to do it, " he told ITV News.
OL,11,F"But, if you're going to hold an
OL,12,Finquest, I sincerely hope that things
OL,13,Fdo come out of it."
OL,15,FPublic and private hospitals Paterson
OL,16,Fworked for have already paid out
OL,17,Fmillions of pounds in compensation.
