OL,6,FOur investigation has also found that
OL,7,FSpire Healthcare - which runs the
OL,8,Fprivate hospitals where Paterson
OL,9,Foperated - has set aside an additional
OL,10,F#4.6 million for compensation for
OL,11,F'future claims and costs'. That's on
OL,12,Ftop of the #13.1 million already paid
OL,13,Fout.
